_:N9b89650c4e844ffaa6cd7ec840be2877 <http://schema.org/description> "The Family Justice Council (FJC) helps to get better results for families in the court system, with input from 30 locally based FJCs around the country. FJC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ." .
